"replyTime":"2020-07-22T02:18:10.000Z","msg":"佢都講真係大鳩鑊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-22T02:26:20.000Z","msg":"１）某報創辦人家族，係英國有大量資產<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n２）某報係奶共，不過讀者群係離地廢老，又或者冇文化靠炒賣而致富人士。<br />\n３）愛國是工作需要，不過都要跟讀者走。"},{"pid":"290bc3d50a18d3582a8ab079eed3f5387c0737bb","tid":2119054,"uid":19092,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-22T02:27:19.000Z","msg":"連登業主仲未入黎咬人既<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/abomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/abomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n一味淨係縮係房台圍爐<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/abomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"83efed1a28729cc7dd62a94d52d3fb2c6c881fe5","tid":2119054,"uid":48077,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-22T02:28:27.000Z","msg":"777: 我唔會中計<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a4cb220c427f8529cf23b7d9d7613361bbff8561","tid":2119054,"uid":47259,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-22T02:35:41.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>以往香港作為東西文明的交匯處，食盡「國際飯」，不同文化、不同族群都可在此找到共同利益，令香港展現勃勃生機。</blockquote><br />\n宜家無咗呢個誘因變成支那城市咁人哋走晒都好合理呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"00792a7f09cd01329795a6ea35a5b010c85bbb79","tid":2119054,"uid":263485,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-22T03:18:35.000Z","msg":"香港，夕陽下的小漁村。"}]}